gle_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573787783"&gt;&lt;div class="embed-responsive embed-responsive-16by9"&gt;&lt;iframe allowfullscreen="" class="embed-responsive-item" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/1EuWYOjmfXg?wmode=transparent" wmode="Opaque"&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://youtu.be/1EuWYOjmfXg?si=85lKYxKvTwNd2OD5" target="_blank"&gt;https://youtu.be/1EuWYOjmfXg?si=85lKYxKvTwNd2OD5&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;咁即係仲有排跌啦&lt;img alt="" border="0" smilieid="31" src="https://www.discuss.com.hk/images/smilies/default2/smile_04.gif"&gt;&lt;a class="postmorevideochannel" href="videochannel.php" title="進入香討影片區"&gt;進入香討影片區&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=32019998&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=194746226568b35e1d996669_86631019"/><published>2025-08-30T10:35:46+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>2bfbeab6562a90bd4850bd12fb78edfc</id><title>葉秀亮預測又中，公司開始減薪，今次卜街了</title><updated>2025-08-30T11:43:17+08:00</updated><author><name>hkduck123</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-08-30T11:43:17+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573788607"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573788607"&gt;有保安公司開始減薪，或者減工作日數。&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;信和替更保安都要減人工 25% &lt;span style="font-size:22px;"&gt;😅&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;「為配合勞工法例468要求，將會於10月份開始對散工有新安排&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;1⃣方案1：&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;薪金不變，前後的4個星期內，工作不能超過5天&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;2⃣方案2：&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;薪金不變，合約期為59天（59天內不限返工日數，可返足59天）約滿後需要停工一個月方可重新簽約&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;3⃣方案3：薪金需要調低，簽1年合約，可享有一般勞工法例上的福利，例如：有薪法定假期,有薪年假、合約滿後，需要停工一個月後，才可以再簽新合約，薪金大約每日減150至200元。」&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=32020066&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=194746226568b35e1d996669_86631019"/><published>2025-08-30T11:43:17+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>4f75b41f6981e36daec28046377cfe0b</id><title>［特首sell海德園］ 李家超今日視察愛東邨 與街坊握手傾談及了解區內情況</title><updated>2025-08-30T12:03:10+08:00</updated><author><name>海邊笨拙的榴槤</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-08-30T12:03:10+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573788836"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573788836"&gt;特首出動sell海德園&lt;br&gt; 李家超今日去了港島東視察愛東邨與街坊握手傾談及了解區內情況&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://r.discuss.com.hk/link.php?url=https%3A%2F%2Fportal.sina.com.hk%2Fnews-hongkong%2Fnews-realtime%2Frthk%2F2025%2F08%2F30%2F1283573%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E8%25B6%2585%25E8%25A6%2596%25E5%25AF%259F%25E7%25AD%25B2%25E7%25AE%2595%25E7%2581%25A3%25E6%2584%259B%25E6%259D%25B1%25E9%2582%25A8%25E3%2580%2580%25E8%2588%2587%25E8%25A1%2597%25E5%259D%258A%25E6%258F%25A1%25E6%2589%258B%25E5%2582%25BE%25E8%25AB%2587%25E5%258F%258A%25E4%25BA%2586%25E8%25A7%25A3%2F&amp;amp;platform=&amp;amp;uhash=5bfc9f0131651442d87dc0bd78f9dffc&amp;amp;fid=110" target="_blank"&gt;https://portal.sina.com.hk/news- ... 察筲箕灣愛東邨與街坊握手傾談及了解/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=32020085&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=194746226568b35e1d996669_86631019"/><published>2025-08-30T12:03:10+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>82eb5a5e01decd5ad75f2fcd73abdabb</id><title>🔥🔥🔥香港淪為大陸二線城市 連深圳都不如❓❗️😂🤣</title><updated>2025-08-30T18:32:23+08:00</up